INSERT INTO `proposal` (`id`, `projectid`, `background`, `just_element`, `objectives`, `cust_require`, `project_impact`, `methodology`, `scope`, `deliverables`, `critical_path`, `milestones`, `human_resource`, `facilities`, `statutory`, `reference`, `date_proposal`, `target_schedule`, `target_costing`, `target_organisation`, `target_proposal`, `justification_element`) VALUES
(0, '880349-2018-01', '<p>It is predicted that by the year of 2080, the supply of oil will be running out. This invention provides an energy-dependable source for cars, which is renewable.</p>\r\n', 'Formulation & design of possible new or improved product or process alternatives', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Type</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Customer Analysis</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Definition</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Non-functional requirement\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Performance Requirement</li>\r\n			<li>Operational Requirement</li>\r\n			<li>Quality Requirement<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '<ol>\r\n	<li>Agile Methodology</li>\r\n	<li>Scrum Methodology</li>\r\n	<li>XP Methodology</li>\r\n	<li>PMI&#39;s PMBOK Methodology</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>This project will consist of creating an electric-generated vehicle that can be charged within a 10 minute interval. The project will be completed by 2022.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Path A = 1460 days</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path B = 1295 days</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path C = 1400 days&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path D = 1320 days&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Critical path = Path A</p>\r\n', '', '', '<ol>\r\n	<li>Meeting Room</li>\r\n	<li>Server Room</li>\r\n	<li>Power Grid</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>ISO/FDIS 9001:2015 QMS Standard requires an organization to determine and control the statutory and regulatory requirements applicable to the organization&rsquo;s products and services. It is the responsibility of the organization to demonstrate compliance within its quality management system. On perusal this ISO/FDIS 9001: 2015 QMS Standard, we find, in the introduction part of the standard indicates that this standard, can be used by internal and external parties. So it is imperative for th', '', '2018-02-22', 'upload/schedule/', 'upload/costing/', 'upload/organisation/RESOURCES REQUIRED.docx', 'upload/proposal/', '<p>We proposed a new incentive for vehicles to function. Vehicles, especially cars, are predicted to be double in its amount by 2040. This is concerning since the world&#39;s number one source of fuel is petroleum. Even when gas can be used to reduce the usage of petroleum-based fuel, it still won&#39;t be enough. By using electric-based incentive, the source won&#39;t be running out since electricity can be generated using various things, including charcoal. This research needs to be funded to find a formulation to enable fast charging method for vehicles in every charging station.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
(0, '880252-2018-01', '<p>In 2007, Google joined forces with the mobile industry to form the Open Handset Alliance (OHA). The mission was to establish Android as an open-source OS. This meant anybody could access, download and modify Android`s source code for free to help develop apps, mobile device, or even a competing OS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android`s open platform helps people around the globe enjoy greater access to more information and opportunity than ever before.</p>\r\n', 'Formulation & design of possible new or improved product or process alternatives', '', '', '', '<p>Waterfall Model</p>\r\n', '<p>There are two places that scope is defined on your project. high level scope is defined in your project charter.Low level scope is defined in your business requirements document.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Path A&nbsp;=&nbsp; 150 Days</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path B&nbsp;=&nbsp; 170 Days</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path C&nbsp;= 178 Days</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '<p><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family:source serif pro,serif; font-size:21px">ISO/FDIS 9001:2015 QMS Standard requires an organization to determine and control the statutory and regulatory requirements applicable to the organization&rsquo;s products and services. It is the responsibility of the organization to demonstrate compliance within its quality management system. On perusal this ISO/FDIS 9001: 2015 QMS Standard, we find, in the introduction part of the standard indicates t', '', '2018-02-22', 'upload/schedule/', 'upload/costing/', 'upload/organisation/', 'upload/proposal/Doc1.docx', '<p>Produce highly optimize battery usage in android OS.</p>\r\n'),
(0, '10022759-2018-01', '<h1><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:open sans; font-size:14px">TNB Research Sdn. Bhd., better known as TNBR, has been the in-house solution provider for Tenaga Nasional Berhad (TNB) since 1993. Situated in Kajang, Selangor, the Research &amp; Development (R&amp;D) Centre, provides a centralised, one-stop centre for technical solutions and innovation.</span></h1>\r\n', 'Search for application of research findings or other knowledge', '', '<ol>\r\n	<li>Type\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Customer Analysis</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Definition\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Performance Requirement</li>\r\n		<li>Operational Requirement</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', '<p>Waterfall model</p>\r\n', '<p>There are two places that scope is defined on your project. High level scope is defined in your project charter. Low level scope is defined in your business requirements document.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Path A = 120&nbsp;days&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path B = 150 days&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path C = 170 days&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Path D = 140 days</p>\r\n', '', '<p>Project Sponsor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Project Owner</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Project Manager</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Steering Commiteee</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Team Member</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stakeholder</p>\r\n', '<p>Hardware&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Software</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other</p>\r\n', '<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-size:21px">Statutory requirements are those requirements which are applicable by virtue of law enacted by the government</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-size:21px">A regulatory requirement can be termed as administrative legislation that constitutes or constraints rights and allocates responsibilities.&nbsp;', '', '2018-02-23', 'upload/schedule/', 'upload/costing/', 'upload/organisation/', 'upload/proposal/', '<h2>To help improving&nbsp;the accessibility of TNBR current staff system more&nbsp;efficiency.</h2>\r\n'),
