(1, '880349-2018-01', 'Titan', 'Level 1', 'Value creation is the primary aim of any business entity. ', 'Assumptions and exclusions are the specific disclaimers and decisions about the project that are used to clarify project scope. It is important to clarify high level assumptions and define scope boundaries so stakeholders understand the scope of the project. By defining the project scope assumptions upfront, it generates conversation to further detail.', 'RM30000', 'RM25000', 'RM20000', 'RM15000', 'RM10000', '2018-02-22'),
(2, '880252-2018-01', 'Power Management in Android Devices', 'Level 1', 'Able to produce an efficient battery that are able to sustain longer battery life and at the same time a battery that highly resistance than the current one.', 'Cost of Researching = (RM2000 x No of worker)\r\nCost of repair (workmanship, materials, etc) = RM 50 \r\nCost of Maintenance = (RM 40 x per item) \r\nTotal estimated value creation =  (Cost of researching + cost of repair + cost of maintenance)', 'RM8000.00', 'RM10000.00', 'RM12000.00', 'RM13000.00', 'RM15000.00', '2018-02-22'),
(3, '10022759-2018-01', 'TNBR Staff Mobile Application', 'Level 2', 'All of TNBR staff can access all of the company information easily with their smartphones everywhere.  This mobile application is much better than the current system that all of the staff are currently using because they don''t need any personal computer (PC) to access to the system. Plus, the smartphone is smaller compared to PC and it is very easy to bring it everywhere. ', 'Cost of repair (workmanship, materials, etc) = RM 100\r\nCost saving due to ease of installation = RM  50 (Rate per hour per team x 3 hours) \r\nCost Maintenance per month = RM 500\r\nTotal estimated value creation = 10 000', 'RM 3000', 'RM 3000', 'RM 2000', 'RM 1000', 'RM 1000', '2018-02-22'),
